## 1ï¸âƒ£ Single-cast Delegate

Points to ONE method.

```csharp
delegate void MyDelegate();

class Demo
{
    static void A() => Console.WriteLine("Method A");

    static void Main()
    {
        MyDelegate d = A;
        d();   // Calls A only
    }
}
```

---

## 2ï¸âƒ£ Multicast Delegate

Points to MULTIPLE methods.

```csharp
delegate void MyDelegate();

class Demo
{
    static void A() => Console.WriteLine("A");
    static void B() => Console.WriteLine("B");

    static void Main()
    {
        MyDelegate d = A;
        d += B;
        d();   // Calls A then B
    }
}
```

---

## 3ï¸âƒ£ Generic Delegates (Built-in)

C# provides ready-made delegates:

### âœ… Action

* No return value

```csharp
Action<string> print = msg => Console.WriteLine(msg);
print("Hello");
```

### âœ… Func

* Returns a value

```csharp
Func<int, int, int> add = (a, b) => a + b;
Console.WriteLine(add(5, 3));
```

### âœ… Predicate

* Returns bool

```csharp
Predicate<int> isEven = x => x % 2 == 0;
Console.WriteLine(isEven(4));  // true
```

